# TC15: LowBatteryDetected1
# Precondition: NormalMode, cleaning in progress
# Action: detect battery level below threshold
# Expected: enter LowBatteryMode, cleaner and motor deactivate
power
start
expect power on
expect mode NormalMode
expect cleaner on
expect motor moving
battery 5
low-battery
expect power on
expect mode LowBatteryMode
expect battery 5
expect motor stopped
expect motorForward false
expect cleaner off
expect cleanerMode off
exit
